OL,6,EClub 140Bgoes on an investigative foray
OL,7,Bbehind the headlines of those spicy    
OL,8,Bshowbiz stories. Are they news or      
OL,9,Bnonsense?                              
OL,11,ETABLOID RUMOUR:BBoyzone'sERonan Keating
OL,12,Bis to co-host this year's Eurovision   
OL,13,BSong Contest, to liven it upE(The Sun).
OL,15,ECLUB 440 TRUTH:B"Yes it's true,"       
OL,16,Bconfirms Boyzone's PR Kate Stewart.    
OL,17,B"He's looking forward to it. He has had
OL,18,Bsome experience presenting on Top of   
OL,19,Bthe Pops, so he isn't nervous."        
