OL,6,ETABLOID RUMOUR:BTheESpice GirlsBgot all
OL,7,Bdolled up to play a prank on record    
OL,8,Bcompany bosses in America. They were   
OL,9,Bforced to pull out of a meeting at the 
OL,10,Blast minute, so sent five inflatable   
OL,11,Bdolls in theirBplaceE(Daily Star).     
OL,13,ECLUB 440 TRUTH:B"It's an old story     
OL,14,Bthat they sent the dolls," says their  
OL,15,Brecord company PR. "It's part of the   
OL,16,BSpice mythology, and I'm not sure if   
OL,17,Bit's true, though I'd like to think it 
OL,18,Bis," he adds.                          
