OL,6,ETABLOID RUMOUR:BBoyzone hunksERonan    
OL,7,EKeatingBandESteve GatelyBmay quit the  
OL,8,Bband for careers as movie stars. Top   
OL,9,BHollywood directors have head-hunted   
OL,10,Bthem and the Irish five-piece could    
OL,11,Bsplit as a resultE(Daily Star).        
OL,13,ECLUB 440 TRUTH:B"There have been loads 
OL,14,Bof rumours circulating recently," says 
OL,15,Bthe 'Zone's press person. "First it's  
OL,16,Bthat Ronan's going solo, then it's that
OL,17,BSteven's acting. It's all made-up and  
OL,18,Ball rubbish. They don't call us to     
OL,19,Bcheck the stories like they should."   
