OL,6,ETABLOID RUMOUR:BTheESpice GirlsBhave   
OL,7,Bbubbled up their bank accounts by #1m  
OL,8,Beach after shooting a secret TV ad for 
OL,9,BPepsi. So far the lucrative lasses have
OL,10,Bpocketed #3,220,000 each since they    
OL,11,Bshot to fameE(Daily Star).             
OL,13,ECLUB 440 TRUTH:B"I can't confirm or    
OL,14,Bdeny the Pepsi story," says their PR,  
OL,15,Bmysteriously. "How much they earn is   
OL,16,Bconfidential and the Star's figures are
OL,17,Bpure speculation and not factual at    
OL,18,Ball." But he adds: "They do make a lot 
OL,19,Bfrom merchandise and royalties."       
