OL,6,ETABLOID RUMOUR:EElton JohnBisBthrowing 
OL,7,Ba massive party for his 50th birthday  
OL,8,Band has writen a blank cheque to a     
OL,9,Bmanagement team to fund the bash. He   
OL,10,Bcould splash out as much as #500,000   
OL,11,Bfor the party in London's Hammersmith  
OL,12,BPalais on April 6thE(The Mirror).      
OL,14,ECLUB 440 TRUTH:B"There's no question of
OL,15,Ba blank cheque," says a spokesman for  
OL,16,Bthe Elton John Aids Foundation. "There 
OL,17,Bisn't a budget for the party. The date 
OL,18,Band the place are right but the money  
OL,19,Bdetails are wrong," he adds.           
